{
  "stem": "18778.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We were asked to help the farmers when it got to be spring, and we would be on the fields by 5 o'clock, picking peas and picking berries and whatever.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And they paid us a few pence per bushel, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And so, and my-- my landlord also-- let me-- he was the shoemaker.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And he had me carrying out shoes that he fixed for people, and he paid me a few pennies for each pair of shoes.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "So I was able to give my mother money so she could use it for carfare to go to various offices downtown to get my father ready for our immigration.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Because meanwhile, our number had come up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Our papers were in England.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "We could leave if we would know how to get out of there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "There was also a question of paying the fare.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "You see, what-- we didn't have any money.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And we wanted to get out of England.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And there's correspondence that I found in my mother's papers about the monies that people paid for the immigration-- the immigration certificates issued by the Cuban government, which were not-- declared not legal.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "You see, I didn't touch upon that before.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "The Cuban immigration officer-- his name was Gonzales-- had simply printed these immigration permits on official looking stationery.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And he sold them for whatever-- he sold them through another party.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Many of them were refugees living in Cuba.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "He probably sold them to these people for a set sum of money, and then these people were selling them to us for whatever they could get.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What happened after we got to England was that a lot of people wrote to my father and said, couldn't he, in some way, try to get that money back?",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because we never used the permits.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
